1
00:00:25,025 --> 00:00:26,108
Huh?

2
00:00:26,192 --> 00:00:27,525
A person that I love?

3
00:00:27,608 --> 00:00:28,608
[RIFANA]
Mm-hmm.

4
00:00:28,692 --> 00:00:31,108
Do you have anyone
special like that?

5
00:00:31,192 --> 00:00:33,067
Um... Uhh...

6
00:00:34,442 --> 00:00:35,442
There's my dad.

7
00:00:35,525 --> 00:00:36,483
How's that?

8
00:00:36,567 --> 00:00:37,692
[RIFANA sighs]

9
00:00:37,775 --> 00:00:40,483
[RIFANA] That's not
what I'm talking about.

10
00:00:40,567 --> 00:00:42,192
So what about you, Rifana?

11
00:00:42,275 --> 00:00:43,775
Do you have someone?

12
00:00:44,983 --> 00:00:47,025
There's no one yet,

13
00:00:47,108 --> 00:00:51,150
but I wanna marry someone like
one of the legendary heroes.

14
00:00:51,233 --> 00:00:53,692
Someone like the Shield Hero?

15
00:00:53,775 --> 00:00:55,942
I've wanted to meet him forever!

16
00:01:02,025 --> 00:01:03,983
[RAPHTALIA, RIFANA scream]

17
00:01:05,150 --> 00:01:06,567
Hey, look!

18
00:01:14,983 --> 00:01:16,942
Please! Spare me!

19
00:01:17,025 --> 00:01:18,817
Have mercy on me.

20
00:01:20,067 --> 00:01:21,483
After killing so
many demi-humans

21
00:01:21,567 --> 00:01:23,483
in that underground
chamber of yours,

22
00:01:23,567 --> 00:01:25,192
you dare beg for your life?!

23
00:01:25,275 --> 00:01:26,567
You're not--

24
00:01:26,650 --> 00:01:27,942
It can't be!

25
00:01:28,025 --> 00:01:30,400
One of my enslaved villagers?

26
00:01:30,483 --> 00:01:32,025
An animal like you?

27
00:01:32,108 --> 00:01:33,817
A damned demi?!

28
